data.description: This beautiful home is currently 2 units but SUPER easy (open up by removing a door) to convert back to one home or occupy one & rent out the other! The first side offers an open floor plan w/ wood-burning fireplace, beamed ceilings & new LVP floors. The kitchen is modern & stylish. The primary bedroom features concrete floors, a jetted tub & ample closet space. Outside, there's a covered patio, RV parking & new storage shed. The highlight is the pool w/ new pump.  The other side features concrete floors, fresh paint & a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The kitchen boasts new appliances, Mexican tile countertops & large pantry. Enjoy an Arizona room in the front & an extra room for an office or kids' playroom. Skylights fill the space w/ natural light. Plus, mountain views from the front!
